ZH: 这里种植水果的人不使用化肥。
EN: The farmers here do not use chemical fertilizer for growing fruits.

ZH: 这种化肥对植物的生长有很大的帮助。
EN: This chemical fertilizer greatly helps the growth of plants.

ZH: 政府鼓励农民使用有机肥代替化肥。
EN: The government encourages farmers to use organic fertilizers instead of chemical ones.

ZH: 长期使用化肥会导致土地贫瘠。
EN: Long-term use of chemical fertilizers can result in soil depletion.

ZH: 家庭菜园里用不着使用过多的化肥。
EN: There is no need to use excessive chemical fertilizers in a home garden.

ZH: 化肥的用量需要根据作物需求来调整。
EN: The amount of chemical fertilizer used should be adjusted according to the needs of the crops.

ZH: 许多农民都选择使用化肥来提高作物产量。
EN: Many farmers choose to use chemical fertilizers to increase crop yields.

ZH: 这种化肥虽然价格高，但效果很好。
EN: Although this chemical fertilizer is expensive, it is very effective.

ZH: 有机农业不使用化肥和农药。
EN: Organic farming does not use chemical fertilizers and pesticides.

ZH: 化肥的使用应该适量而不过量。
EN: The use of chemical fertilizers should be moderate and not excessive.

ZH: 这块土地已经被过度施用化肥。
EN: This piece of land has been overused with chemical fertilizers.

ZH: 有机庄园里不允许使用化肥。
EN: Chemical fertilizers are not allowed to be used on organic farms.

ZH: 每个季节合适的化肥种类都不尽相同。
EN: The suitable type of chemical fertilizer varies in each season.

ZH: 农民们很少在秋季施用化肥。
EN: Farmers rarely apply chemical fertilizers in the autumn.

ZH: 合理使用化肥可以增加作物品质。
EN: Proper use of chemical fertilizers can improve the quality of crops.

ZH: 这里所生产的化肥质量有保障。
EN: The quality of the chemical fertilizers produced here is guaranteed.

ZH: 化肥施用方式应依据土地条件而定。
EN: The application of chemical fertilizers should be based on the condition of the soil.

ZH: 不要在台风季节施用化肥。
EN: Do not apply chemical fertilizers during typhoon season.

ZH: 这家农场使用了大量的有机肥而不是化肥。
EN: This farm uses a lot of organic fertilizers instead of chemical ones.

ZH: 化肥对土壤有害处，但也有好处。
EN: Chemical fertilizers can be harmful to the soil, but they also have benefits.
